Addictive game. Simple concept but very tactical. AI gets really nasty later on,  very hard to beat. Campaigns are nearly impossible! Don't be fooled by the simple idea... you have to plan your actions and hasty moves are quickly punished... 1.30am... just one more game... could do with a mute option on the start screen rather than buried in the menu.

Love this game, cannot put it down despite completing the ranks, I start over and over. Increasing rank doesnt seem to increase difficulty. The game unfortunately is too easy which is why I gave only 4 stars. More islands would be great as some levels there are only about 7 so the level is pretty much over in 10-15 seconds. overall very good game, few tweaks could make this a strategic masterpiece.
